      <title>The Fiancé</title>
      <link>http://bluevisual.tv/work/thefiance/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Sep 2015 21:05:29 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://bluevisual.tv/work/thefiance/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Firebreathing Films asked me to do moderate VFX work for &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.imdb.com/title/tt4159698/&#34;&gt;The Fiancé&lt;/a&gt;, a horror movie.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34;&gt;
  &lt;video width=&#34;960&#34; height=&#34;540&#34; autoplay loop muted controls&gt;
    
      &lt;source src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/videos/thefiance-video-01.mp4&#34; /&gt;
    
  &lt;/video&gt;
  
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;A majority of the shots were placing glowing eyes on various characters via motion tracking.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle2&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-02.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Glowing eyes&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle2&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle2&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle2&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-02.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Glowing eyes&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-03.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;More glowing eyes&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-03.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;More glowing eyes&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle4&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-04.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle4&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle4&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle4&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-04.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Other times I rotoscoped cars out of backgrounds and reflections as to not be distracting, or placed a few elements into the scenes.
&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle5&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-05.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Replacing Jack in the Box signs&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle5&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle5&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle5&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-05.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Replacing Jack in the Box signs&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One of the more creative and fun scenes to do was adding a projected image into a certain scene.
&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle1&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-01.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Closeup of a final composted frame&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle1&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle1&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle1&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-01.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Closeup of a final composted frame&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This was my process:
1. Rotoscope the foreground to create an alpha matte
2. Project the screen onto the background
3. Cast shadows by subtracting an offset version of the foreground alpha channel from the backdrop.
4. Project an offset and distorted image onto the characters
5. Place the character projections back on using the foreground&amp;rsquo;s alpha matte&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle6&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-06.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;With and without composited projection screen&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle6&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle6&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle6&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-06.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;With and without composited projection screen&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle7&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-07.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Final composited frame from a further angle back&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle7&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle7&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle7&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/thefiance-07.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Final composited frame from a further angle back&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
