  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://bluevisual.tv/images/honeyglue-03.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;The bee model with an Inverse Kinematics system&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
